data.description:
Welcome home to this wonderful 4 bedroom, 3 bath brick home on a very
private 1.59 lakefront, preserve lot in Waterford Estates built by Trademark Homes in 2001 with 2512 square feet of living space. Fantastic floor plan with office, Florida room, & 2nd owners suite orbonus/media room. Interior features include entry foyer, French doors, wood floors, plantation shutters, round corner bead, upgraded lighting, arched doorways, custom moldings, niches, water softener, ceiling fans, custom interior paint, ceramic tile, inside laundry with built in cabinets, recessed lighting, wired for surround sound, security system, niches, granite in baths, knock down ceiling texture, & fireplace with mantle. Gourmet kitchen has 42 inch raised panel cabinets with crown molding, rubbed bronze hardware, display shelves, built in desk, & pull out shelves, granite  counter tops, breakfast bar, walk in pantry, bay window in nook, deep sink with sprayer feature, tile backsplash, refrigerator, dishwasher, smooth top range/self cleaning oven, & built in microwave.  Private owners suite has ceiling fan, tray ceiling, his & her walk in closets, ceramic tile, garden tub, separate shower with glass block, & dual shower heads, his & her granite vanity with framed mirrors above, medicine cabinet, linen closet, & enclosed water closet.  Exterior features include full brick exterior, decorative glass door & water feature at entry, side entry 3 car garage with automatic opener, attic stairs, & epoxy finish on floor, paver lanai, sprinkler system, vinyl soffits, gutters, & architectural shingle roof. Outstanding Mandarin location makes this a great place to call home.  To see this property call Debbie today!
